Included scripts were run in a fiqat python venv.

Rough script commands from my use:
Extracting bbox coords:
(fiqat_venv) m@ubuntu:/m/OFIQ-Project/python/bbox_and_face_crop$ python3 extractBoundingBoxes.py --input /m/images/custom/ --output_csv bbox_custom.csv

Cropping using bbox coords above:
(fiqat_venv) m@ubuntu:/m/OFIQ-Project/python/bbox_and_face_crop$ python3 preprocess_CropFaces.py --csv bbox_custom.csv --input-root /m/images/ --output-dir /m/preprocessed_images/minimal_preprocess_crop --margin 0.20 --top-extra 0.15 --square --resize 518 --report-csv crop_report_CUSTOM.csv
